1
00:01:03,740 --> 00:01:05,880
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,180 --> 00:01:09,920
[Episode 7]

3
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:13,200
[Yunshao Hall]

4
00:01:20,430 --> 00:01:22,560
You really do take things as they come.

5
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:32,150
Is this the first day
Your Majesty has known me?

6
00:01:32,150 --> 00:01:34,080
If you wanted tears and hysterics,

7
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:36,280
I'm afraid you'll be disappointed.

8
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:44,280
Will you let me go?

9
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:46,880
Let you go?

10
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:49,759
You'll live here from now on.

11
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,090
You're not going anywhere.

12
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:55,039
Xie Jiuzhao,

13
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:56,840
are you putting me under house arrest?

14
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:59,170
Have you thought about the consequences?

15
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:02,430
Say it again.

16
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,200
Say what?

17
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:07,690
That was the first time
you called me by name.

18
00:02:07,850 --> 00:02:08,430
You...

19
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,750
Yeah.

20
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,240
You are the exalted Emperor.

21
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,630
You can ignore consequences
whenever you want.

22
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:16,710
But have you ever spared a thought

23
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,630
for what happens to me?

24
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,240
That night,

25
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:23,360
you walked away from Zhao
without looking back.

26
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,430
Then I, too, can act as I see fit.

27
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,190
You don't want to get married?

28
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:30,630
Fine. I'll make sure of it.

29
00:02:30,630 --> 00:02:32,310
Even if you stay out of the palace,

30
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:35,310
you won't marry anyone else.

31
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,910
I may not want to get married,

32
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,240
but you don't get to decide that for me.

33
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,700
You don't get a say in this.

34
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,430
Her Highness ordered us
to do whatever it takes

35
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:49,470
to kill that Jiang girl.

36
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,910
I'll say it one last time.

37
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,870
From today on,

38
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:56,150
without my permission,

39
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:58,800
you are not to step outside this chamber.

40
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,080
Miss Jiang,

41
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,100
these are gifts from His Majesty.

42
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,710
Take the clothes.

43
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:24,079
Leave the rest.

44
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:27,490
Please don't make things
difficult for us, Miss Jiang.

45
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:30,630
I... I'm just telling you what I want.

46
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,400
How is that making things difficult?

47
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,680
His Majesty has decreed

48
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:36,800
that we must dress you personally.

49
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,630
Otherwise...

50
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,520
Just leave it.

51
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,910
I'll change later.

52
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,450
We shall take our leave.

53
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,470
Xingzhi?

54
00:04:12,470 --> 00:04:12,930
This...

55
00:04:12,930 --> 00:04:14,550
[Xingzhi]

56
00:04:19,220 --> 00:04:21,390
[Moonlit Spectacle]

57
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:27,720
[Moonlit Spectacle]

58
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,180
Greetings, Your Majesty.

59
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:35,830
General Xun, what brings you
to see me today?

60
00:04:35,890 --> 00:04:36,040
[Moonlit Spectacle]

61
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,950
Your Majesty,

62
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:39,000
my wedding's coming up,

63
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:42,830
so I hoped to ask for
a bit of imperial favor.

64
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:46,830
I've heard

65
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:49,920
that my bride, Li, is fond of opera.

66
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,680
I'd like to purchase
Wenxiang Pavilion outright

67
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:55,480
and request that Your Majesty
grant it a new name.

68
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,820
Once it's renovated,

69
00:04:57,870 --> 00:05:00,330
I plan to give it to her
as her betrothal gift.

70
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:03,510
What do you think, Your Majesty?

71
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:08,830
The Wenxiang Pavilion?

72
00:05:09,770 --> 00:05:11,780
I do enjoy their wine.

73
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:11,870
[Moonlit Spectacle]

74
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:12,920
I'm just afraid

75
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:16,040
it won't be the same place

76
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,630
once it's yours.

77
00:05:18,430 --> 00:05:19,830
So Your Majesty

78
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,870
won't grant my request?

79
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:26,720
You still have time to plan a wedding?

80
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,390
Looks like you don't know

81
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:30,720
that your dear aunt tried to

82
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,750
have Jiang Li killed just days ago.

83
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,510
Your Majesty must be joking.

84
00:05:34,510 --> 00:05:35,480
I never joke.

85
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:38,610
-But she is just an ordinary...
-And that's exactly why!

86
00:05:45,310 --> 00:05:46,800
Remember this.

87
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:49,830
Anyone you can't protect,

88
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:50,830
I will.

89
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,000
I won't pursue this today.

90
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,430
So get out of my sight now.

91
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:09,040
I'll take my leave.

92
00:06:24,870 --> 00:06:25,630
Aunt!

93
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:26,600
General Xun.

94
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,270
Aunt!

95
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:28,160
General Xun.

96
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,210
Out of my way!

97
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:31,750
General Xun...

98
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:35,000
Please help me, Aunt.

99
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,350
What's wrong?

100
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:38,120
Xie Jiuzha

101
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,720
knew perfectly well that Li and I
are formally betrothed,

102
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,190
yet he took her anyway.

103
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:43,600
This humiliation is unbearable.
Aunt, you must

104
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,870
help me take Li back!

105
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:47,600
Simo, do you have proof?

106
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:49,600
He didn't even try to hide it.

107
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,130
What more proof do you need?

108
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:55,390
This cannot be handled rashly.

109
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,310
Right now,

110
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,630
it's not worth

111
00:06:57,630 --> 00:06:59,120
offending the Emperor

112
00:06:59,120 --> 00:06:59,950
for a tutor's daughter.

113
00:06:59,950 --> 00:07:01,600
But she is my wife-to-be!

114
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,720
It's only a matter of time anyway.

115
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,630
I could kill

116
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:09,450
Xie Jiuzhao this very moment!

117
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:10,240
Enough!

118
00:07:10,870 --> 00:07:12,950
Everything must serve the greater cause.

119
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:14,310
Are you prepared

120
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,870
to drag us all to our deaths

121
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:17,160
for one woman?

122
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,000
So your "greater cause"

123
00:07:21,870 --> 00:07:23,510
means I swallow all the pain?

124
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:27,600
Or did you never want me
to marry Jiang Li at all?

125
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:29,630
You agreed on the surface,

126
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:32,090
then tried to have her killed
behind my back!

127
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:40,430
Her reputation is already ruined.

128
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:42,480
Why obsess over her?

129
00:07:43,510 --> 00:07:45,800
Your parents want you to marry

130
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,720
a respectable woman from a great family.

131
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,750
I'll choose someone better.

132
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,310
As for the Emperor,

133
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,950
now isn't the time.

134
00:07:57,830 --> 00:07:59,950
I see it now.

135
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:04,830
You and Xie Jiuzhao are the real family.

136
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,870
All this concern for me

137
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:09,270
was just using me for power.

138
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,390
He humiliates me,

139
00:08:11,390 --> 00:08:12,480
and I'm still expected to endure it.

140
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,190
Then tell me. What am I?

141
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:20,950
Simo!

142
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,830
Simo!

143
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:40,909
Chuanmo.

144
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:41,840
Huaijin.

145
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:48,000
Did anyone see you?

146
00:08:48,970 --> 00:08:49,080
[Former Left General of Zhao State,
Xun Chuanmo]

147
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,000
The imperial decree has been issued.

148
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:54,130
I'll be taken into the palace soon
as one of his consorts.

149
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,480
Right now,

150
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,480
all I can do is stall,

151
00:08:58,870 --> 00:09:00,530
hold on until the baby is born.

152
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:02,600
Since your marriage to Yu

153
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,480
is already decided...

154
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,550
this child

155
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:14,220
will be yours and hers.

156
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,870
I'll submit a petition tomorrow.

157
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:17,510
There might still be a chance. We...

158
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:19,670
No one else can ever know about this.

159
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,200
What His Majesty wants

160
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:25,670
is for my family to help him
keep the court in check.

161
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,870
You've seen what happened
to my father

162
00:09:28,870 --> 00:09:30,000
when he crossed him.

163
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:34,030
You can't risk your entire family for me.

164
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:53,030
Once remembered, never forgotten.

165
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,240
Let's

166
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,790
name the child Simo.

167
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:13,840
You are our child.

168
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:20,680
How could I not plan for you?

169
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,120
Jiang Li.

170
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,360
Jiang Li?

171
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:38,360
Jiang...

172
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,140
It actually looks good on you.

173
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,480
What?

174
00:10:52,150 --> 00:10:54,080
You thought I was trying to escape?

175
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,610
And would you, if you could?

176
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,360
I might make it out of the chamber,

177
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,840
but not beyond the palace gates.

178
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,870
So why waste my time?

179
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,870
You'd better not.

180
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,320
By the way,

181
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:12,050
I wanted to ask you something.

182
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,870
There's a name on a painting
I found here, Xingzhi.

183
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:16,480
Is he one of the palace artists?

184
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:17,720
Where is he now?
